29-30 Beniwɑ bɑ kuɑ Horibɑn bwese kɛrin wiruɡibu Edɔmun temɔ, Lotɑni kɑ Sobɑli kɑ Sibeoni kɑ Anɑ kɑ Disoni kɑ Esɛɛ kɑ Disɑni.
Nɡe mɛyɑ u kɑ Yosɛfu ɡɔrɑ Sikɛmuɔ sɑɑ Heboronin di.
Ye u Onɑni sɑrɑsiɑ, u kpɑm wure u ɡurɑ suɑ u bii tɔn durɔ mɑrɑ, mɑ bɑ nùn yĩsiru kɑ̃ Selɑ. Sɑɑ yè sɔɔ kurɔ wi, u Selɑ mɑrɑ, Yudɑ u ǹ wɑ̃ɑ mi. U dɑ u wɑ̃ɑwɑ Kisibuɔ.
Sɑnɑm mɛ kurɔ wi, u mɑrubu turɑ yerɑ bɑ wɑ mɑ sikɑbɑrɑ bɑ wɑ̃ɑ win nukurɔ.
Wiruɡii wi, u ku rɑ mɛɛri ye Yosɛfu u mɔ̀ domi Yinni Gusunɔ u wɑ̃ɑ kɑ wi. Mɑ u derɑ win ye u kuɑ kpuro yɑ wɛ̃rɑ.
Doo wii sɑko si, su doo wii ɡeenu mwɛ mwɛ. Mɑ u dom yɑndɑ u deemɑ u dosɑwɑ.
Yerɑ u bu bikiɑ u nɛɛ, mɑnɑ sɑ ko mɑɑ tɔnu wɑ wi u Gusunɔn Hunde mɔ nɡe wini.
Bɑ nùn wisɑ bɑ nɛɛ, ɑɑwo, yinni, sɑ nɑwɑ su kɑ dĩɑnu dwe.
Rubɛni u ben tundo wisɑ u nɛɛ, ɑ ɡesi mɑn Bɛnyɑmɛɛ nɔmu sɔndio. Nɑ̀ kun kɑ nùn wurɑmɛ, nɛn bibu yiru wee, ɑ bu ɡoowo.
Bɑ nùn wisɑ bɑ nɛɛ, bɛsɛn tundo, wunɛn bɔ̃ɔ u wɑ̃ɑ hunde sɔɔ, u bwɑ̃ɑ do.
Ye sɑ yeni ɡeruɑ, yinni, mɑ ɑ nɛɛ, su kɑ nùn nɑ wunɛn mi, ɑ nùn wɑ kɑ nɔni.
Ye u Bɛnyɑmɛɛ yɔ̃su, yerɑ u win mɑɑ ben bɑɑwure bɔkɑsi u sɔ̃su u kɑ swĩisimɔ. Yen biruwɑ bɑ kɑ nùn ɡɑri kuɑ.
Beni kɑ sere win bii tɔn kurɔ Dinɑ bɑ sɑ̃ɑ Leɑn bibu be u Yɑkɔbu mɑruɑ Pɑdɑnɑrɑmuɔ. Be kɑ ben bibu bɑ sɑ̃ɑwɑ mi tɔnu tɛnɑ kɑ itɑ.
Mɑ Yɑkɔbu u kpɑm sunɔ domɑru kuɑ bɑ sere yɑrɑ win min di.
Nɑ yeni mɔ̀wɑ yèn sɔ̃ nɑ wunɛn mɛro Rɑsɛli kĩ. Ye sɑ wee Pɑdɑnin di u mɑn ɡbiiriwɑ swɑɑɔ Kɑnɑnin temɔ ye n tie fiiko su kɑ Efɑrɑtɑ du. Miyɑ nɑ nùn sikɑ. Efɑrɑtɑ yerɑ bɑ mɔ̀ Bɛtelehɛmu.
