I wɛ̃ro tɔ̃ɔ wɛ̃rɑruɡiru sɔɔ, kpɑ i tu ɡɑrisi te nɑ yi nɛnɛm nɛn sɔ̃.
Wi u tɔnu so u ɡo, bɑ koo yɛ̃ron tii ɡowɑ.
Goo ù n win winsim ɡobi, ǹ kun mɛ ɡɑ̃ɑnu berusiɑ, mɑ bɑ nu ɡbɛnɑ mi u beruɑ mi, bɑ̀ n ɡbɛnɔ wi wɑ ye u suɑ min nɔn yiruwɑ u koo kɔsiɑ.
Ì n mɑɑ win kɛtɛku wɑ ɡɑ wɔrumɛ kɑ sɔmunu, i ku doonɑ i nùn deri. I nùn somiɔ i kɑ ɡu seeyɑ.
Wunɛ Mɔwisi, kɑɑ mɑn susimɑ wunɛ turo. Be bɑ kɑ nun yɔɔmɑ bu yɔ̃ro mi bɑ wɑ̃ɑ mi. Tɔn be bɑ mɑɑ tie, bu ku rɑɑ yɔɔmɑ mini.
Sumi yi sɔɔrɑ dɑ̃ɑ pɔɔsi yi, yi ko n dɑ n wɑ̃ɑ. Bɑ ǹ yi wunɑmɔ min di.
Kpɑ ɑ mɑɑ bekunu wɔkurɑ tiɑ wesi kɑ boo sɑnsu ni bɑ koo kuu bekuruɡii te wukiri.
Kpɑ ɑ ten wɔllun ɡoo ɡɔmkinɔ kɑ̃ɑnu doke kpɑ ɑ nu sii ɡɑndu pote.
Kpɑ ɑ nu mɑni tɑrɑkpe ɡen sɑri sɔɔ. Aroni ù n nu doke win senɔ, niyɑ nu koo sɔ̃ɔsi mɑ kɑ Isirelibɑn yĩsinɑ u duɑ nɛn sɑ̃ɑ yerɔ, kpɑ nɛ, Yinni Gusunɔ nɑ n kɑ bu yɑɑye.
A bu sokoto kpirinu kuo kpɑ bu ku kɑ ben tereru wɑn sɔ̃. Kɑɑ ye kpuro kowɑ kɑ wɛ̃ɛ dɑmɡii.
Kpɑ ɑ yɑ̃ɑ kinɛ ten nɔmu suɑ ɑ yiiyɑ wɔllɔ nɛn wuswɑɑɔ. Nɡe mɛyɑ kɑɑ kɑ sɔ̃ɔsi mɑ ɡuroɡuro te kɑ nɔmu ɡe, yɑ sɑ̃ɑwɑ nɛɡiɑ.
ɑ Isirelibɑ ɡɑrio. Be bɑ wɔ̃ɔ yɛndu turɑn diyɑ kɑɑ ɡɑri kpɑ ɑ de ben bɑɑwure u ɡobi ɡɛɛ wɛ̃ u kɑ win wɑ̃ɑru yɑkiɑ. Kpɑ n de wɑhɑlɑ yu bu suuri sɑɑ ye ɑ bu ɡɑrimɔ mi.
U koo kpĩ u yen kpunɑɑbɑ yi. U wurɑn sɔmburu yɛ̃, kɑ sii ɡeesu kɑ sii ɡɑndu.
Sɑɑ yerɑ Mɔwisi u sɑrɑmɑ ɡuu ten wɔllun di u woodɑn kpee bɛsi yiru ye nɛni yèn beri yiru yiru kpuro bɑ yoruɑ.
Ù n duɑ mi, sɑɑ yerɑ ɡuru wii wuro te, tɑ rɑ sɑrɑmɛ tu yɔ̃rɑ kuu ten kɔnnɔwɔ kpɑ Yinni Gusunɔ u kɑ nùn ɡɑri ko.
Sɔrɔkudo i ko bɛɛn bii tɔn durɔbu kurɔbu suɑ ben bii wɔndiɑbɑ sɔɔ, kpɑ kurɔ be, bu de bɛɛn bii be, bu nɛn sɑ̃ɑru deri bu tɔn ben bũnu sɑ̃.
kɑ kpee ɡobiɡinu nìn nɔni sɑ̃ɑ bɛrɔ wuru ni bɑ koo doke yɑbe tɑrɑkpe ɡe sɔɔ, kɑ ni bɑ koo doke bɔɔ bɑrɑ yen wɔllɔ.
Mɑ tɔn be bɑ sɔmbu te mɔ̀ mi, ben bɑɑwure u ɡinɑ win sɔmburu deri,
Mɑ bɑ beku kɑreru kuɑ kɑ wɛ̃ɛ dɑmɡii kɑ wɛ̃ɛ yi bɑ wɔ̃kuɑ kɑ burɑ kɑ mɑɑ ɡɑɑdurɑ, kɑ wɛ̃ɛ wunɔmɡii. Mɑ bɑ wɔllun kɔ̃sobun weenɑsibu kuɑ beku te sɔɔ, yɑ kuɑ ten burɑru.
Mɑ bɑ dɑ̃ɑ pɔɔsi yi kuɑ kɑ ɑkɑsiɑn dɑ̃ɑ bɑ yi wurɑ pote.
