Yen biruwɑ Abinɛɛ u mɑɑ Dɑfidi sɔ̃ɔwɑ u nɛɛ, yinni sinɑ boko, kon se n dɑ n Isirelibɑ kpuro mɛnnɑ kpɑ bu kɑ nun ɑrukɑwɑni bɔke bɑ n kɑ wunɛn ɡɑri sɔmburu mɔ̀. Kpɑ ɑ n bɑndu dii be sɔɔ, ɑ n mɔ̀ ye ɑ kĩ.
Yerɑ tɔn be, bɑ kɑ Isi Bosɛtin wii te dɑ Dɑfidin mi, Heboroniɔ, bɑ nɛɛ, wunɛn yibɛrɛ Sɔɔlu wi u kɑsu u nun hunde wunɑ, win bii Isi Bosɛtin wiru wee. Yinni Gusunɔwɑ u Sɔɔlu kɑ win bweseru mɔru kɔsie ɡisɔ wunɛn sɔ̃.
Dɑfidi u kpɑm Isirelibɑn tɑbu durɔbu kpuro sokɑ u mɛnnɑ bɑ kuɑ tɔmbu nɔrɔbun subɑ tɛnɑ (30.000).
Yen sɔ̃, ɑ doo ɑ Dɑfidi nɛn sɔm kowo sɔ̃ ɑ nɛɛ, nɛ Gusunɔ wɔllu kɑ tem Yinni, nɛnɑ nɑ yeni ɡerumɔ. Yɑ̃ɑ kpɑrɑbun diyɑ nɑ nùn wunɑmɑ u n kɑ sɑ̃ɑ nɛn tɔmbu Isirelibɑn kpɑro.
