Mɑ Sibɑ u nùn wisɑ u nɛɛ, yinni, kɛtɛku nini, nu sɑ̃ɑwɑ ni wunɛn yɛnuɡibu bɑ koo sɔni. Pɛ̃ɛ yeni kɑ dɑ̃ɑ bii nini, yɑ sɑ̃ɑwɑ ye wunɛn tɑbu kowobu bɑ koo di. Be bɑ mɑɑ wɑsirɑ ɡbɑburɔ, tɑm mɛniwɑ bɑ koo nɔ, kpɑ bu dɑm wɑ.
Wunɛn tii, ɑ wunɛn tundo kɑ win tɔmbu yɛ̃ mɑ bɑ sɑ̃ɑwɑ tɑbu durɔbu. Bɑ kɔ̃ruɑwɑ nɡe ɡbeeku yɑɑ ɡɔbɑ ye bɑ binu mwɑɑri. Yen biru ɑ yɛ̃ mɑ wunɛn tundo wi, u sɑ̃ɑwɑ tɑbun sɑriɑ yɛ̃ro. U ǹ wurɑmɔ u kpunɑ kɑ tɔn be sɑnnu.
