kɑ Simuri kɑ Yeyɛli Elisɑfɑnin bibun bweseru sɔɔ kɑ Sɑkɑri kɑ Mɑtɑniɑ Asɑfun bibun bweseru sɔɔ
Mɑ bɑ derɑ bɑ kpɑrɑ Isirelin tem kpuro sɔɔ sɑɑ Beri Sebɑn di n kɑ dɑ sere Dɑnuɔ, tɔmbu bu kɑ nɑ Yerusɑlɛmuɔ bu Gusunɔ Isirelibɑn Yinni Gɔɔ sɑrɑribun tɔ̃ɔ bɑkɑ te diiyɑ. Domi tɔn dɑbiru tɑ ku rɑ rɑɑ mɑɑ tu di nɡe mɛ bɑ yoruɑ bu ko.
Mɑ Esekiɑsi u yɑ̃ku kowobu kɑ Lefi be bikiɑ u nɛɛ, subu nirɑ̀ mini.
Sɑnkeribu u tireru yoruɑ u kɑ Gusunɔ Isirelibɑn Yinni wɔmɛ. U nɛɛ, nɡe mɛ bwese ni nu tien bũnu nu ǹ kpĩɑ nu nin tɔmbu wɔre win nɔmɑn di, nɡe mɛyɑ Gusunɔ, Esekiɑsin Yinni u ǹ mɑɑ kpɛ̃ u bu wɔrɑ win nɔmɑn di.
Mɑ Yinni Gusunɔ u ɡɔ̃ru ɡɔsiɑ u win kɑnɑru mwɑ, u kɑ nùn wurɑ Yerusɑlɛmuɔ win bɑndu sɔɔ. Sɑɑ ye sɔɔrɑ Mɑnɑse u ɡiɑ mɑ Gusunɔwɑ u sɑ̃ɑ Yinni.
Yen biru, yɑ̃ku kowo Hilikiyɑ u mɑɑ mɑn tireru ɡɑru wɛ̃.
Yen biruwɑ bɑ ben tiiɡiɑ kɑ yɑ̃ku kowobuɡiɑ yikuɑ. Domi yɑ̃ku kowo Aronin bibu bɑ sɔmburu kuɑ sere kɑ wɔ̃kurɔ. Bɑ yɑ̃ku dɔ̃ɔ mwɑɑrɑruɡinu kɑ yɑɑ ɡum yɑ̃kunu mɔ̀. Yen sɔ̃nɑ Lefibɑ bɑ bu yɑɑ yikuɑmmɛ.
Nɛbukɑnɛsɑɑ u Yinni Gusunɔn sɑ̃ɑ yerun ɑrumɑni ɡurɑ bɑkɑ kɑ piibu kɑ ben sinɑ kpɑɑrun ɑrumɑni kɑ sinɑ bokon tiiɡiɑ kɑ sere mɑɑ win sinɑ bwɑ̃ɑbuɡiɑ.
Biɡifɑin bweseru sɔɔ, bɑ sɑ̃ɑwɑ tɔmbu nɔrɔbun subɑ yiru kɑ weerɑɑkuru kɑ nɔɔbɑ tiɑ (2.056).
kɑ Kɛrɔsi kɑ Siɑɑ kɑ Pɑdoni
Nɡe mɛyɑ sɑɑ suru nɔɔbɑ yirusen tɔ̃ɔ ɡbiikirun di, bɑ Yinni Gusunɔ yɑ̃ku dɔ̃ɔ mwɑɑrɑruɡinu kuɑmmɛ bɑɑ mɛ bɑ ǹ ɡinɑ sɑ̃ɑ yee ten kpɛɛkpɛɛku swĩi.
Sɑɑ ye sɔɔ, Gusunɔn sɔmɔ Asee kɑ Sɑkɑri Idon bii bɑ Gusunɔn ɡɑri ɡeruɑ kɑ Gusunɔ Isirelibɑn Yinnin yĩsiru Yerusɑlɛmuɔ kɑ Yudɑbɑn tem kpuro sɔɔ.
Gusunɔn sɔmɔbu Asee kɑ Sɑkɑri, Idon bii bɑ Isirelibɑn wiruɡibu dɑm kɑ̃ bɑ kɑ sɑ̃ɑ yee te bɑnɑ bɑ kpɑ mɑm mɑm. Bɑ tu bɑnɑwɑ nɡe mɛ Gusunɔ Isirelibɑn Yinni u ɡeruɑ kɑ nɡe mɛ Pɛɛsin sinɑm beni, Sirusi kɑ Dɑrusi kɑ Aɑtɑsɛsi bɑ yen woodɑ yi.
Ɛsidɑrɑsi u nɛɛ, i Gusunɔ bɛsɛn bɑɑbɑbɑn Yinni siɑro. U derɑ sinɑ boko u win sɑ̃ɑ yee te tɑ wɑ̃ɑ Yerusɑlɛmuɔ bɛɛrɛ wɛ̃.
kɑ ɡbɛ̃ɛ bɑsilɑnu yɛndu ni bɑ kuɑ kɑ wurɑ. Yen ɡeerɑ sɑ̃ɑwɑ wurɑn ɡobi nɔrɔbu (1.000) kɑ sere boo sii ɡɑnduɡisu yiru si su bɑllimɔ. Boo si, su kɑ wurɑɡisu bɛɛrɛ nɛwɑ.
Yen biru, Ɛsidɑrɑsi u yɑrɑ Gusunɔn sɑ̃ɑ yerun di u dɑ Yokɑnɑni Eliɑsibun biin dirɔ. Sɑnɑm mɛ u duɑ mi, u ǹ dĩɑnu di, u ǹ mɑɑ nim nɔrɑ. Domi win nuki sɑnkire Isireli be bɑ yoru mwɛɛrɑn dɑɑ kɔ̃sɑ ye bɑ kuɑn sɔ̃.
